textfsm_template:
Value CounterType (\S+)
Value TotalPackets (\d+)
Value InputICMP (\d+)
Value InputICMP_Fail (\d+)
Value InputICMP_Dhist (\S+)
Value OutputICMP (\d+)
Value OutputICMP_Fail (\d+)
Value ActiveConnOpen (\d+)
Value PassiveConnOpen (\d+)
Value FailedConn (\d+)
Value ResetRecvConn (\d+)
Value EstablishedConn (\d+)
Value SegmentsIn (\d+)
Value SegmentsOut (\d+)
Value RetransSeg (\d+)
Value BadSeg (\d+)
Value ResetSent (\d+)
Value UdpPacketsIn (\d+)
Value UdpPacketsOut (\d+)

Start
  ^Ip:
  ^\s+${CounterType} total packets received -> StartIpCount
  ^Icmp:
  ^\s+${CounterType} ICMP messages received -> StartIcmpCount
  ^IcmpMsg:
  ^\s+OutType3: ${OutputICMP}
  ^Tcp:
  ^\s+${CounterType} active connection openings -> StartTcpCount
  ^Udp:
  ^\s+${CounterType} packets received -> StartUdpCount

StartIpCount
  ^\s+${TotalPackets} total packets received
  ^Icmp: -> StartIcmpCount
  ^Tcp: -> StartTcpCount
  ^Udp: -> StartUdpCount

StartIcmpCount
  ^\s+${InputICMP} ICMP messages received
  ^\s+${InputICMP_Fail} input ICMP message failed
  ^ICMP input histogram:\s*$$
  ^\s+destination unreachable: ${InputICMP_Dhist}
  ^ICMP messages sent
  ^\s+${OutputICMP} ICMP messages sent
  ^\s+${OutputICMP_Fail} ICMP messages failed
  ^IcmpMsg: -> Next
  ^Tcp: -> StartTcpCount
  ^Udp: -> StartUdpCount

StartTcpCount
  ^\s+${ActiveConnOpen} active connection openings
  ^\s+${PassiveConnOpen} passive connection openings
  ^\s+${FailedConn} failed connection attempts
  ^\s+${ResetRecvConn} connection resets received
  ^\s+${EstablishedConn} connections established
  ^\s+${SegmentsIn} segments received
  ^\s+${SegmentsOut} segments sent out
  ^\s+${RetransSeg} segments retransmitted
  ^\s+${BadSeg} bad segments received
  ^\s+${ResetSent} resets sent
  ^Udp: -> StartUdpCount

StartUdpCount
  ^\s+${UdpPacketsIn} packets received
  ^\s+${UdpPacketsOut} packets sent
  ^UdpLite:
  ^TcpExt: -> Record
